        public Void doOperation(DeleteAnalytic operation,
                        uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.Context context,
                        uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.Store store)
                 throws uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.OperationException
        Deletes an Analytic from the cache specified in the Operations Declarations file (assuming the user has write privileges on the specified Analytic). The user needs only to provide the name of the operation they want to delete.
        Specified by:
        doOperation in interface uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.operation.handler.OperationHandler<DeleteAnalytic>
        Parameters:
        operation - the Operation to be executed
        context - the operation chain context, containing the user who executed the operation
        store - the Store the operation should be run on
        Returns:
        null (as output of this operation is void)
        Throws:
        uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.operation.OperationException - thrown if the user doesn't have permission to delete the Analytic
